Weeks after a photo was posted on Breaking Amish the Truth showing cast members Rebecca and Abe with a 
baby, Rebecca revealed she is divorced and confirmed she is a mother.

But on the show's finale on Sunday, she refused to name the father of the baby. While Abe is rumoured to be the dad, the couple claims they only started dating on the show.

'I'm very sensitive when it comes to my 
daughter because I'm trying to be a good mom,' Rebecca said as she refused to
talk about her child. 'I don't have to answer to anybody.'

She continued: '[Fans] can believe whatever they 
want, but if they want to know, they can watch the show. If they don't 
want to believe, they don't have to believe it.

