'I don't give a s***
what anybody thinks. People have to discuss our lives so much that we 
can't even have our own life anymore. They're making us out to be 
somebody I don't even know.'

But while the couple refused to go into further details, friends have not been so shy, 
revealing that Rebecca and Abe lived together while she was pregnant.

'They stayed in a camper behind our 
home for several months in 2010 while Rebecca was pregnant with their 
baby girl,' Shannon Edwards, from Columbia, Kentucky told the National 
Enquirer.

It has already been revealed that Rebecca left her first husband, Rufus Hostetler, to start a relationship with Abe in 2010. She was also filmed marrying Abe on the show.

Rebecca was not to silent on other aspects of her former life, revealing that her teeth appeared different in earlier photos as she has since had them all removed and replaced with dentures.

